<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <title>Responsive Webpage</title>

    <style>

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: rgb(205, 225, 232);
        }

        header {
            background-color: rgb(71, 71, 171);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #333;
        }

        nav a {
            color: rgb(202, 131, 131);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: block;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        main {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {

    
            body {
                background-color: rgb(167, 110, 110);
            }

        
            main {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            nav a {
                border-top: 1px solid #444;
            }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>My Responsive Website</h1>
        <p>Resize the browser to see changes</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Services</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <h2>Welcome</h2>
        <p>
            <p>
                  Welcome to our website! We are excited to have you here. 
                  This platform is designed to provide useful information, helpful resources, and a smooth user experience. 
                  Explore the content, discover new ideas, and feel free to connect with us for any support or queries.
            </p>
        </p>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
